@@TJvScrollText.Pause
Summary
  Pauses scrolling the text.
Description
  Call Pause to pause scrolling the text. Pause will decrease ScrollPixels until its equal to 0.
See Also
  Reset, ScrollPixels, Unpause
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollText.Reset
Summary
  Resets the text position.
Description
  Call Reset to reposition the text to it's start position.
See Also
  Pause, Unpause
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollText.ScrollDirection
Summary
  Determines how text is scrolled within the control.
Description
  The possible values of ScrollDirection are

  <TABLE>
    Value               Meaning
    -----               -------
    drFromLeft          Text is scrolled from left to right.
    drFromRight         Text is scrolled from right to left.
    drFromTop           Text is scrolled from top to bottom.
    drFromBottom        Text is scrolled from bottom to top.
  </TABLE>
See Also
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollText.ScrollPixels
Summary
  Determines the amount of pixels the text is moved per scroll event.
Description
  Use ScrollPixels to set the number of pixels that the text will move per refresh. If ScrollPixels is 0,
  the text on the control won't move at all. 
    
  The default value for ScrollPixels is 1.
See Also
  Delay
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollText.TextAlignment
Summary
  Determines how the scroll text is aligned within the control.
Description
  The possible values of Alignment are

  <TABLE>
    Value               Meaning
    -----               -------
    taLeftJustify       Text is aligned at the left of the control.
    taCenter            Text is centered in the control.
    taRightJustify      Text is aligned at the right of the control.
  </TABLE>
See Also
  Items
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollText.Unpause
Summary
  Resumes scrolling the text.
Description
  Call Resume to resume scrolling the text. Resume will increase ScrollPixels until its equal to the value
  specified by the user.
See Also
  Pause, Reset, Unpause, ScrollPixels
